T1  - Pareto Inferior Trade
PY  - 1984
Y1  - 1984/01/01
DO  - 10.2307/2297701
JO  - The Review of Economic Studies
JA  - Rev Econ Stud
VL  - 51
IS  - 1
SP  - 1
EP  - 12
SN  - 0034-6527
AB  - The paper shows that between two competitive but risky economies with no insurance markets, free trade may be Pareto inferior to no trade. The model is simple enough to show clearly the role prices play in transferring and sharing risk when there is an incomplete set of markets, but rich enough to exhibit the resulting inefficiencies dramatically.
Y2  - 3/25/2024
UR  - https://doi.org/10.2307/2297701
ER  - 



